Package: roller
Title: Creates Device and Roll objects to simulate dice rolling
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: MK Larson, marykathrynlarson@berkeley.edu, github: mklarsonn
Description: The purpose of this package is to simulate rolling a die and getting the outputs with different sample sizes.
            Using the device object and roll object, you can customize the roll and then see the visualization of
            the relative frequencies in a plot.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
